text: Wang Ying (born 15 February 1984) is a Chinese taekwondo practitioner. She won a silver medal at the 2003 World Taekwondo Championships. She won a gold medal in flyweight at the 2005 World Taekwondo Championships in Madrid, by defeating Brigitte Yagüe in the final.
